SUMMARY:Monday Wake Up ride-BI ARC Second Loop 31F 
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nCue and GPX link: [ARC Se
 cond Loop](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/bi-arc-second-loop-31f
 /)\n\nStart the week off with a Morning Ride. Estimated pace 15mph\n\nHelm
 ets are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (
 spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nWe require LBC Club memb
 ership and Meetup RSVP to join this ride.\nBeing on Meetup does not mean y
 ou are a club member.[Join the Club](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/con
 tent.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148)\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide
  by the club's:\n[Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/co
 ntent.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\n[Rules of the Road
 ](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257
 148&module_id=325159)\n[Ride Waiver](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/docs.as
 hx?id=763523)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3139989
 83/
