SUMMARY:Wednesday Morning's Breakfast Rides  Casual Pace Variable Distance
  RSVP
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nIt' Spring! Time to chang
 e 9am.\nEvery Wednesday morning...Ride and eat Yummy breakfast together. A
 round 25 miles.\nPlease do not go on this ride unless you will ride at a c
 asual pace and stay with the group . We will meet to ride to breakfast at 
 a casual pace. After eating some may split up with some returning to the s
 tart and others going longer and faster.\nHelmets are mandatory\; No ear b
 uds or audible music playing devices. Please bring water\, and a basic rep
 air kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\nTo eliminate pass
 ing around a pen and paper waiver\, we encourage LBC Club membership and M
 eetup RSVP below to join this ride. RSVP also allows us to contact you aft
 er the ride if needed. If you do not RSVP you are not covered by the club 
 excess accident insurance policy\; only club members who RSVP are covered.
  Being on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. Join here- https://w
 ww.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148\nRichard C
 onner\, leader717-572-8480
