SUMMARY:IMPROPMTU- LI - West of Lititz (25F)-- RSVP required
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nRide Leader: Bruce Black\
 n\nA mostly flat ride heading west and north of Lititz. The pace will be b
 etween 14 and 16mph with multiple stop and regroup points.\n\n• “short
 ” stop for refreshment/coffee near the end of the rider at New Holland C
 offee Shop **in Lititz**.\n\nThis ride is a social ride\, but cyclists are
  not expected to stay in one group. Cyclists may pedal at their own comfor
 table paces. Please be supportive of the other cyclists to avoid anyone bi
 king alone or being dropped off the back of the last group.\n\nClick for[ 
 Ride with GPS](https://ridewithgps.com/routes/54403730?privacy_code=dbJPe2
 XJITajsx85LEsaBlaITdP37Oif)\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No ear buds. Please 
 bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 in
 flator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we requir
 e LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\nBeing on
  Meetup does not mean you are a club member. [Join here](https://www.lanca
 sterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is 
 your agreement to abide by the club's [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikecl
 ub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984
 ) \,\n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.asp
 x?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159) \, and [Ride Waiver](https:/
 /lancasterbikeclub.net/docs.ashx?id=454318)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3139806
 26/
